channel.title: YoshxV2 RELEASED 317 - Everything is ADDED - player owned SHOPS
channel.description:
YES YES YES, I'm releasing this after being asked thousands of times. I'm going to include what... 2 gifs? yeah sure :D. The server has some glitches, all dupes were patched, enjoy it. If I dont get any comments or rep I WILL remove D:<. K heres the GIF Images. [img]http://ploader.net/files/60b49dcbcb7a28b558406278824bc3de.gif[/img] [img]http://ploader.net/files/25923b80fe873fb0aa3842cc76ad870f.gif[/img] [center]http://www.mediafire.com/?4j84qzl7vf9p0a5 [/center] I really could not be fucked with to add them onto the forum, too much work D:. Some Features! - Godwars (All Monsters and Maps) - Lolno, I lied, we never got around to that. - Custom Minigames - Dungeoneering Armour - Chaos Elemental - King Black Dragon (new models and animations) - 24/7 Server - Chaotic Weapons
- All Working Skills (for a 317) - Duel Arena working 100% - Skillcape Emotes - Friendly Staff Enjoy <3
